    java.lang.Comparable<DXPParameterDefinition<?>>

    public class DXPParameterInstance<T extends java.lang.Comparable<?>>
extends DXPParameterDefinition<T>
    An instance of a DXPParameterDefinition object. If no value is given to this instance, it will take its default value from the DXPParameterDefinition supplied.
